      "seed": 127868101,
      "version": 44,
      "versionNonce": 1579319525,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1769876514377,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Variables (nœuds)\n\nR : Spatial resolution (dpi)\n\nF : Acquisition frequency / interval\n\nT : Taxon identity (ou groupe : Enchytraeidae / Acari / Collembola)\n\nA : True activity near the scanner (non observée)\n\nD : Detectability / detection process (non observée)\n\nY : Observed detections per image (votre réponse principale)\n\nS* : Apparent size proxy (bounding-box area / size)\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
